'''Majdi Smiri''' (wavutse 1983), akunze '''kwitwa Maguy''', ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Tunisiya|Tuniziya]] . <ref>http://www.tunivisions.net/34528/560/548/majdi-smiriun-artiste-complet-et-comble.html</ref> Yatangiye umwuga we nk'umuraperi, bidatinze Smiri yabaye umuyobozi ukunzwe wa filimi zizwi cyane za televiziyo ''Talaa Wala Habet'', ''Lilet Chak'' na ''Case 460'' .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1983 i Tuniziya, muri [[Tuniziya]]. <ref>https://elcinema.com/en/person/1004953/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga we nk'umuraperi ku izina rya Maguy<ref>https://femmesdetunisie.com/interview-de-maguy-a-majdi-smiri/</ref>. Yanditse, arahimba nyuma akora Njoum Ellil muri duet hamwe numuririmbyi Ines Chkimi<ref>https://stringfixer.com/fr/Majdi_Smiri</ref>. Mu 2006, yagaragaye bwa mbere muri sinema hamwe na firime ''Making of'' iyobowe na Nouri Bouzid. Nyuma yaje kubona impamyabumenyi mu Ishuri ry'Ubuhanzi na Sinema muri Tuniziya. Hanyuma yimukiye mu Bufaransa maze akora umwaka umwe mu ruganda rukora ibicuruzwa. Amaze gusubira muri [[Tuniziya]], yashinze uruganda rwe rukora amajwi n'amashusho, 'Underground Skills', mu 2007. Binyuze muri sosiyete, yayoboye amashusho yindirimbo nyinshi hamwe niyamamaza. Hanyuma yayoboye ibiganiro bya tereviziyo nka ''Koujinitna'' kuri tereviziyo y'igihugu, ''Urban Fen'' kuri TV ya Hannibal na ''Ser El'' Benna kuri TV ya Coujina. <ref>https://www.jetsetmagazine.net/FR.1.magazine.interviews.interview_exclusive_avec_majdi_smiri_confinement.1404</ref><ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5298041/bio</ref>

Muri 2009, yakinnye nka 'Farid', umukanishi n'umuraperi, muri ikinamico ''Njoum Ellil'' iyobowe na Madih Belaïd. <ref>https://www.tuniscope.com/article/5200/harrer-el-wakt/fil-talvza/ferid-de-njoum-ellil-</ref> Muri 2012, yakoze filime ye yambere ''yumukobwa, Fausse Note'' aho yari umwanditsi akaba na producer. Muri 2015, Smiri yahawe igihembo cyerekezo cyiza cy'ikinamico ''Lilet Chak'' muri Romdhane Awards, yatanzwe na Mosaïque FM. <ref>http://archivev2.mosaiquefm.net/fr/index/a/ActuDetail/Element/55005-romdhane-awards-2015-le-prix-de-la-meilleure-realisation-revient-a-lilet-echak</ref> Muri 2015, yanditse amagambo  ya Lilet Chak, yahimbwe na Yacine Azaiez kandi yaririmbwe na Chkimi. Muri 2016, yayoboye urukurikirane rwa tereviziyo ''Bolice'' yatsindiye igihembo cyurukurikirane rwiza muri Romdhane Awards. <ref>https://www.mosaiquefm.net/fr/actualite-culturel-tunisie/19693/romdhane-awards-la-meilleure-serie-est-bolice-0-2</ref>

